0_rule_text: Jagermeister is intended for adults of legal purchase age that can be specific for different countries (e.g. 18 in EU and 21 in the US).
1_rule_text: Jagermeister encourages responsible decision-making regarding the consumption of alcohol in appropriate places.
2_rule_text: Avoid subtle, indirect, or unintentional discrimination against members of a marginalized group.
3_rule_text: Respect and acknowledge the origins and traditions of all cultures and avoid cultural appropriation.
4_rule_text: Jagermeister discourages abusive consumption of alcohol.
